an></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/cpmB2ha</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LogicDude]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A raise would’ve been more appropriate.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EbWHjst</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SSlRGq9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://edition.cnn.com/2024/11/15/media/scientific-american-editor-resignation/index.html</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/EbWHjst</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MyVerySmarterUserName]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Refunds</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1czgNX3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ysiz2V4.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/1czgNX3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Arcturus1976]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Adorable, but also extremely dangerous!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IlkTffH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dTGzS43.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Seriously folks, secure your animals while the vehicle is in motion. Take it from a former animal control officer. In the event of a crash we'd much rather pick up your animal and keep them safe while you go to the hospital, it's not fun picking them up in a body bag.

Info requested regarding good ways to secure your pets.
You want a full chest harness that attaches at the front of the animal close to the center of gravity. For smaller dogs they have like half box deals that fully buckle in and have a tether inside to attach to your harness (search dog booster seat the AKC brand one that I've had for a long time works great for small dogs seen a few negative reviews of the same product just now when looking it up so maybe quality has declined?) For big dogs just the harness and a tether that clips into a seatbelt. Loose enough that they can adjust their sit/stand position but taught enough they cant leave one person's worth of seat or get off the seat onto the floor. There are some extra large dog booster seats, but I can't attest to their efficacy. All in all dog car seats do more to keep your dog comfortable and less likely to want to wiggle around. The number one thing is keeping your animal from flying around the cabin in a crash. 

For your cats, a STURDY crate that you can secure with a normal over the shoulder seatbelt is my personal recommendation.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IlkTffH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Necridos]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Shamelessly, immediately stolen; bc of perfection.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Kt2Wnrs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MP3WGvE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Guys, pay attention! :)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Kt2Wnrs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[hiyo365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>America first mugshots</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uER6BSc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WOXuRsK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uER6BSc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[wafflesdidit]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Best Combat Sport :)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/hREBIbt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VkfbNyk.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hREBIbt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Luvlyquants]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Little boy is so hungry..</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ESZztBu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3DnW5yH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ESZztBu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HimetiLighting]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>*plap*plap*plap*plap*plap*plap*plap*plap*plap*</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Pjo83kk</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6w1qT4o.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><g